      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 21.54,
      "end": 23.06,
      "text": "ASOP's Fables",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 24.62,
      "end": 26.8,
      "text": "The Ass and the Shadow",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 27.58,
      "end": 33.42,
      "text": "A certain man hired an ass for a journey in summertime and started out with the owner",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 33.42,
      "end": 35.48,
      "text": "following behind to drive the beast.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 36.26,
      "end": 42.5,
      "text": "By and by, in the heat of the day, they stopped to rest, and the traveler wanted to lie down",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 42.5,
      "end": 43.46,
      "text": "in the ass's shadow.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 44.32,
      "end": 49.0,
      "text": "But the owner, who himself wished to be out of the sun, wouldn't let him do that.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 49.84,
      "end": 52.78,
      "text": "For he had hired the ass only and not his shadow.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 52.78,
      "end": 59.36,
      "text": "The other maintained that his bargain secured him complete control of the ass for the time being.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-013",
      "start": 60.24,
      "end": 65.76,
      "text": "From words, they came to blows, and while they were belaboring each other, the ass took to his heels",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-014",
      "start": 65.76,
      "end": 67.52,
      "text": "and was soon out of sight.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-015",
      "start": 70.36,
      "end": 73.68,
      "text": "End of the Ass and His Shadow of ASOP's Fables",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
